{"tid":2246589,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印媒專訪台灣外交部部長  胡錫進:中國可以支持印度東北部錫金分離主義者復國","createTime":"2020-10-17T07:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T08:08:09.000Z","uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e12268d4ecbf5670a6d91860c7fb356e921255e6","tid":2246589,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印度媒體《今日印度》（India Today）周四（10/15）播出一段專訪台灣外交部長吳釗燮的影片後，立刻又讓中國玻璃心碎。除<strong><span class=\"red\">中國駐印度大使立刻發聲明，要求印度媒體恪守「一個中國」</span></strong>原則外，中國的民間發言人、《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進則是回嗆說，中國可以支持印度東北部的錫金分離主義者復國，報復印度挺台。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進今日（10/17）發文稱：「印度民間一些力量近來頻頻拿台灣問題滋事，囂張地認為他們可以用這個問題踩中國的腳趾，讓中國難受。」胡錫進接著幼稚地建議說：「印度民間力量玩弄台灣問題，<strong><span class=\"red\">但他們要知道，我們可以支援印度東北部的分離主義力量，支持錫金復國，這些都是我們手裡潛在的報復牌。印度民族主義分子需要自重，他們的國家很脆弱。</span></strong>」</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201017/OOIPZZAX6JAWZAEXMYEW3KVBUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201017%2FOOIPZZAX6JAWZAEXMYEW3KVBUY%2F&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=9b2976dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201017%2FOOIPZZAX6JAWZAEXMYEW3KVBUY%2F&h=d725527a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201017/OOIPZZAX6JAWZAEXMYEW3KVBUY/</a>"},{"pid":"ba721fb6e47a2f87e4746931534af2bf108e2402","tid":2246589,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"印度: 我係咪應該驚?"},{"pid":"de0637cc7553289f66f3be348d301fdd42d05743","tid":2246589,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"如果心共真係弱智到支持分離主義，印度人一定將成個喜瑪拉雅山以南全部打哂佢。"},{"pid":"8004eac5ce08d72f37defd021366dfe44b94ac99","tid":2246589,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de0637cc7553289f66f3be348d301fdd42d05743","tid":2246589,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"reply